{
    "verses": [
        {
            "id": 5268,
            "verse_number": 27,
            "verse_key": "67:27",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 225,
            "ruku_number": 499,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَلَمَّا رَأَوْهُ زُلْفَةً سِيٓـَٔتْ وُجُوهُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ وَقِيلَ هَـٰذَا ٱلَّذِى كُنتُم بِهِۦ تَدَّعُونَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101078,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "But when they see it<sup foot_note=197584>1</sup> approaching, the faces of those who disbelieve will be distressed, and it will be said, \"This is that for which you used to call.\"<sup foot_note=197583>2</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 218933,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Kemudian apabila (datang kiamat dan) mereka melihat (azab) yang dijanjikan itu secara dekat, muramlah muka orang-orang yang kafir itu, serta dikatakan (kepada mereka): \"Inilah dia yang dahulu kamu kerap kali minta disegerakan kedatangannya!\"."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096245,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "অতঃপর যখন তারা তাকে (অর্থাৎ ক্বিয়ামতকে) নিকটে উপস্থিত দেখতে পাবে, তখন কাফিরদের মুখ মলিন হয়ে যাবে, আর (তাদেরকে) বলা হবে, ‘এই তো (ও‘য়াদা বাস্তবায়িত হয়েছে) যা তোমরা চাচ্ছিলে।’"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5269,
            "verse_number": 28,
            "verse_key": "67:28",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 225,
            "ruku_number": 499,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُمْ إِنْ أَهْلَكَنِىَ ٱللَّهُ وَمَن مَّعِىَ أَوْ رَحِمَنَا فَمَن يُجِيرُ ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ مِنْ عَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101079,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Say, [O Muḥammad], \"Have you considered:<sup foot_note=197585>1</sup> whether Allāh should cause my death and those with me or have mercy upon us, who can protect the disbelievers from a painful punishment?\""
                },
                {
                    "id": 218934,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Tanyalah (wahai Muhammad, kepada mereka): \"Bagaimana fikiran kamu, jika Allah binasakan daku dan orang-orang yang bersama-sama denganku (sebagaimana yang kamu harap-harapkan), atau Ia memberi rahmat kepada kami (sehingga kami dapat mengalahkan kamu), - maka siapakah yang dapat melindungi orang-orang yang kafir dari azab seksa yang tidak terperi sakitnya?\"."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096246,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "বল, ‘‘তোমরা ভেবে দেখেছ কি আল্লাহ যদি আমাকে আর আমার সঙ্গী সাথীদেরকে ধ্বংস করে দেন অথবা আমাদের উপর দয়া করেন (তাতে তোমাদের লাভটা কী?) মর্মান্তিক শাস্তি থেকে কাফিদেরকে বাঁচাবে কে?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5270,
            "verse_number": 29,
            "verse_key": "67:29",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 225,
            "ruku_number": 499,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "قُلْ هُوَ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ ءَامَنَّا بِهِۦ وَعَلَيْهِ تَوَكَّلْنَا ۖ فَسَتَعْلَمُونَ مَنْ هُوَ فِى ضَلَـٰلٍ مُّبِينٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101080,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Say, \"He is the Most Merciful; we have believed in Him, and upon Him we have relied. And you will [come to] know who it is that is in clear error.\""
                },
                {
                    "id": 218935,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Tegaskan (wahai Muhammad, kepada mereka): \"Allah Dia lah Yang Maha Pemurah, yang kami beriman kepadaNya, dan yang kepadaNya kami berserah diri; oleh itu kamu akan mengetahui kelak siapakah yang berada dalam kesesatan yang nyata\"."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096247,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "বল, ‘তিনিই দয়াময়, আমরা তাঁর উপরেই ঈমান রাখি, আর তাঁর উপরেই নির্ভর করি। তোমরা শীঘ্রই জানতে পারবে কে সুস্পষ্ট গুমরাহীতে আছে (আমরা না তোমরা)।’"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5271,
            "verse_number": 30,
            "verse_key": "67:30",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 225,
            "ruku_number": 499,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُمْ إِنْ أَصْبَحَ مَآؤُكُمْ غَوْرًا فَمَن يَأْتِيكُم بِمَآءٍ مَّعِينٍۭ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101083,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Say, \"Have you considered: if your water was to become sunken [into the earth], then who could bring you flowing water?\""
                },
                {
                    "id": 218938,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Katakanlah lagi: \"Bagaimana fikiran kamu, sekiranya air kamu hilang lenyap (di telan bumi), maka siapakah (selain Allah) yang dapat mendatangkan kepada kamu air yang sentiasa terpancar mengalir?\"."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096248,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "বল, ‘‘তোমরা ভেবে দেখেছ কি যদি তোমাদের পানি ভূগর্ভের তলদেশে চলে যায়, তাহলে তোমাদেরকে কে এনে দেবে প্রবহমান পানি?’’"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5272,
            "verse_number": 1,
            "verse_key": "68:1",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": " نٓ ۚ وَٱلْقَلَمِ وَمَا يَسْطُرُونَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101099,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Nūn.<sup foot_note=197586>1</sup> By the pen and what they inscribe,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 215325,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Nuun. Demi Pena dan apa yang mereka tulis, -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096249,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "নূন, কলমের শপথ আর লেখকেরা যা লেখে তার শপথ।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5273,
            "verse_number": 2,
            "verse_key": "68:2",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "مَآ أَنتَ بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ بِمَجْنُونٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101111,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "You are not, [O Muḥammad], by the favor of your Lord, a madman."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218954,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Engkau (wahai Muhammad) - dengan sebab nikmat pemberian Tuhanmu - bukanlah seorang gila (sebagaimana yang dituduh oleh kaum musyrik, bahkan engkau adalah seorang yang bijaksana)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096250,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমার প্রতিপালকের অনুগ্রহে তুমি পাগল নও।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5274,
            "verse_number": 3,
            "verse_key": "68:3",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَإِنَّ لَكَ لَأَجْرًا غَيْرَ مَمْنُونٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101123,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And indeed, for you is a reward uninterrupted."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218964,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan sesungguhnya engkau tetap beroleh pahala yang amat besar, yang tidak putus-putus, (sebagai balasan bagi menjalankan ajaran Islam);"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096251,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমার জন্য অবশ্যই আছে অফুরন্ত পুরস্কার,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5275,
            "verse_number": 4,
            "verse_key": "68:4",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَإِنَّكَ لَعَلَىٰ خُلُقٍ عَظِيمٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101135,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And indeed, you are of a great moral character."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218986,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan bahawa sesungguhnya engkau mempunyai akhlak yang amat mulia."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096252,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "নিশ্চয়ই তুমি মহান চরিত্রের উচ্চমার্গে উন্নীত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5276,
            "verse_number": 5,
            "verse_key": "68:5",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَسَتُبْصِرُ وَيُبْصِرُونَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101147,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "So you will see and they will see."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218988,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka (tidak lama lagi) engkau akan melihat, dan mereka juga akan melihat, -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096253,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "শীঘ্রই তুমি দেখতে পাবে আর তারাও দেখবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5277,
            "verse_number": 6,
            "verse_key": "68:6",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "بِأَييِّكُمُ ٱلْمَفْتُونُ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101152,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Which of you is the afflicted [by a devil]."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218993,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Siapakah orangnya yang gila di antara kamu semua."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096254,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমাদের মধ্যে কে পাগলামিতে আক্রান্ত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5278,
            "verse_number": 7,
            "verse_key": "68:7",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعْلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ وَهُوَ أَعْلَمُ بِٱلْمُهْتَدِينَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101154,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Indeed, your Lord is most knowing of who has gone astray from His way, and He is most knowing of the [rightly] guided."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218997,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sesungguhnya Tuhanmu, Dia lah jua yang lebih mengetahui akan orang yang sesat dari jalanNya, dan Dia lah jua yang lebih mengetahui akan orang-orang yang mendapat petunjuk."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096255,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমার প্রতিপালক বেশি জানেন কে তাঁর পথ থেকে গুমরাহ হয়ে গেছে, আর সঠিক পথপ্রাপ্তদেরকেও তিনি ভাল করে জানেন।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5279,
            "verse_number": 8,
            "verse_key": "68:8",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَلَا تُطِعِ ٱلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101156,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Then do not obey the deniers."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218999,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Oleh itu (berpegang teguhlah pada ajaran Islam yang sedang engkau amalkan, dan) janganlah engkau menurut kemahuan orang-orang yang mendustakan (ugama Allah)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096256,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "কাজেই তুমি মিথ্যাবাদীদের কথা মান্য কর না।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5280,
            "verse_number": 9,
            "verse_key": "68:9",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَدُّوا۟ لَوْ تُدْهِنُ فَيُدْهِنُونَ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101158,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "They wish that you would soften [in your position], so they would soften [toward you]."
                },
                {
                    "id": 219001,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Mereka suka kalaulah engkau bertolak ansur (menurut kemahuan mereka), supaya mereka juga bertolak ansur berlemah-lembut (pada zahirnya terhadapmu)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096257,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তারা চায় যে, তুমি যদি নমনীয় হও, তবে তারাও নমনীয় হবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5281,
            "verse_number": 10,
            "verse_key": "68:10",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَلَا تُطِعْ كُلَّ حَلَّافٍ مَّهِينٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101100,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And do not obey every worthless habitual swearer"
                },
                {
                    "id": 218962,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan janganlah engkau (berkisar dari pendirianmu yang benar, dan jangan) menurut kemahuan orang yang selalu bersumpah, lagi yang hina (pendapatnya dan amalannya), -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096258,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তুমি তার অনুসরণ কর না, যে বেশি বেশি কসম খায় আর যে (বার বার মিথ্যা কসম খাওয়ার কারণে মানুষের কাছে) লাঞ্ছিত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5282,
            "verse_number": 11,
            "verse_key": "68:11",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "هَمَّازٍ مَّشَّآءٍۭ بِنَمِيمٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101101,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "[And] scorner, going about with malicious gossip -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 214903,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Yang suka mencaci, lagi yang suka menyebarkan fitnah hasutan (untuk memecah belahkan orang ramai), -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096259,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "যে পশ্চাতে নিন্দা করে একের কথা অপরের কাছে লাগিয়ে ফিরে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5283,
            "verse_number": 12,
            "verse_key": "68:12",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "مَّنَّاعٍ لِّلْخَيْرِ مُعْتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ",
            "page_number": 564,
            "juz_number": 29,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 101102,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "A preventer of good, transgressing and sinful,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 219008,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Yang sering menghalangi amalan-amalan kebajikan, yang melanggar hukum-hukum ugama, lagi yang amat berdosa, -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1096260,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "যে ভাল কাজে বাধা দেয়, সীমালঙ্ঘনকারী, পাপিষ্ঠ,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 5284,
            "verse_number": 13,
            "verse_key": "68:13",
            "hizb_number": 57,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 226,
            "ruku_number": 500,
            "manzil_number": 7,
